Class FBICode

java.lang.Object
seng202.group2.model.datacategories.DataCategory
seng202.group2.model.datacategories.FBICode
All Implemented Interfaces:
Categorical, DataClassification, Importable
public class FBICode
extends DataCategory
implements Importable, Categorical
FBI crime code assigned to the crime incident. Used to categorize crime incidents by the type of crime that occurred.

Connor Dunlop
